\sum_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{(x-4)^{n^{2}}}{n!}
3\leq x\leq5
0
x\notin [3,5]
\lim_{n\to\infty}\left|\frac{\,\,\frac{(x-4)^{(n+1)^2}}{(n+1)!}\,\,}{\frac{(x-4)^{n^2}}{n!}}\right|=\lim_{n\to\infty}\left|\frac{n!}{(n+1)!}\cdot\frac{(x-4)^{(n+1)^2}}{(x-4)^{n^2}}\right|=\lim_{n\to\infty}\left|\frac{(x-4)^{2n+1}}{n+1}\right|.
